{
  "stem": "4289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not realize anything, and I thought that my mother betrayed me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what I felt, that she gave me away to the Jews, maybe for money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I saw that those are different people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They did not behave as Catholics.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was so petrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the lady who was supposed to take me to the train station, she was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She wanted to do a mitzvah at that time, as I realized later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she took me on a carriage and horse that was the taxi to the train station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as she went out with me, toward the evening, I started to scream.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People, help, help!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Jews are taking me for matzo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was right probably after the Kielce pogrom because some people stopped us on the street, took sticks, and wanted to beat up the woman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And police came, and the minute she let my hand go, I ran away to the grandfather.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I preferred to go to the grandfather now than to my mother because I felt she betrayed me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I went straight to his house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I came there, he said, oh yes?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's she wanted to do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably take money for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll take care of you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "While this all was happening, the Jewish people in Poland heard about this almost pogrom that I caused in the city of Czestochowa because people at that time were giving used to each other.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were looking for each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow in few days, everybody in Poland knew that I caused some kind of a disturbance in that city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Please describe that disturbance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You said they attacked the woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But what else?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
